{"tid":998280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睡150男後才發現自己是直男　改找女孩「破處」","createTime":"2019-01-28T00:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T03:47:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea95e80f5ebf8a275be92e7a972d4fab911a950","tid":998280,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"英國一名27歲男子，跟150位男性交往已後，才發現自己其實是異性戀。<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，來自英國伯恩茅斯的27歲男子希爾頓（Dominic Hilton），14歲時，覺得自己是同性戀，並且跟家人跟友人坦白，到了18、19歲的時候，他擔任過伴遊男性的工作，也覺得自己以後一定會跟男人結婚，但是到了2017年聖誕節，他跟男友分手後，他決定禁慾一年來摸清自己的性向，沒想到這一摸索，發現男性對他毫無吸引力，反而變得很想去認識女性。<br />\n這一年的單身期，對希爾頓來說是稀有的，因為他至少跟150位男性交往過，幾乎沒有空窗期，「如果你問我人會不會改變性向，過去的我會說沒有」，而有所改變的他，也接受了想法上的改變，「這是一個漸進的過程，需要時間去沉澱一下」。<br />\n希爾頓表示，在這一年中，自己對女性越來越感興趣，「我在想，我或許也有可能是雙性戀，但是我發現男性對我不再有吸引力了，我再也不想跟一個男人睡覺」，現在，希爾頓說他的行為舉止跟穿衣風格都跟以往有很大的差異，且只想找個女性度過一生，希爾頓也鼓勵大家可以嘗試禁慾，專心面對自己內心，讓自己的人生學到不同的事物。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190128/640_8bb7a5f9f556339b38a95add0e4d02ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190128%2F640_8bb7a5f9f556339b38a95add0e4d02ce.jpg&h=50671321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190128/640_18f8c6afae7b976fd2c743c3c9d1ca6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190128%2F640_18f8c6afae7b976fd2c743c3c9d1ca6a.jpg&h=95bb0fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190128/640_a05ba790e9c6dae0b3684c8558a4fc1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190128%2F640_a05ba790e9c6dae0b3684c8558a4fc1f.jpg&h=f30afe48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190128/640_8fcf825141dbdaa876fc58570021ae0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190128%2F640_8fcf825141dbdaa876fc58570021ae0f.jpg&h=eb00aa0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190128/640_862bd4e4871ca225a75bdb0e8474dd14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190128%2F640_862bd4e4871ca225a75bdb0e8474dd14.jpg&h=8f89e6db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74e7fffe535fa7af01819c99560c71eb86d47452","tid":998280,"uid":119610,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"曲到直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1a3df29f0808abd8dec6a7f6a8fbc6e0c9b376","tid":998280,"uid":34241,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:57:41.000Z","msg":"0既盡頭就係1"},{"pid":"5e8a200b92ed2a786fe5c7339190b1a93165887d","tid":998280,"uid":59908,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:59:28.000Z","msg":"屌打金鐘連登仔"},{"pid":"5be99131d6f0ba490dade1466e305ce3e5d783cd","tid":998280,"uid":50658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:00:28.000Z","msg":"靚仔係曲係直有咩所謂"},{"pid":"84395c1bd5fabc2c21b529ccc74cd368fb5885c9","tid":998280,"uid":162567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:01:53.000Z","msg":"咁靚仔，插人又得，被人插都得啦"},{"pid":"61fbe6aef78ea78a1babe75339792e78fd6660f4","tid":998280,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:06:13.000Z","msg":"嚟香港啦 食到你轉返機"},{"pid":"cfbe49293cee00b7f4239c614dc39b1ce7f9feaf","tid":998280,"uid":2429,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"死基佬爭食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f676e0f41c3d5460033f773eea477f2fd4674c5","tid":998280,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:15:26.000Z","msg":"靚仔就冇所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cb4707b2c3e2dbdf3ee1